definition.value: A galactonolactone derived from D-galactonic acid.
A seco-androstane that is 9,10-secoandrostane which is substituted by oxo groups at positions 9 and 17 and in which the A-ring is aromatic and bears hydroxy groups at positions 3 and 4.
Any N-acylethanolamine in which the acyl group has a chain length of C12 or greater.
